First Department,

February, 1947.

(February 3, 1947.) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Mollie Levin, Appellant, against Warden of the Women’s Prison, Respondent.

Order so far as appealed from, dismissing the writ of habeas corpus, unanimously affirmed. Ho opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., Glennon, Dore, Callahan and Peck, JJ.
